	(5432,821,'content_3_big_quote','Prior to joining the RAHU Peer Educators Academy, I was a youth activist and I majorly spoke to young people in my community. I lacked knowledge on how to use social media in my advocacy work. In the Academy, I learnt about how to use social media to increase my efforts in advocating for young peoples SRHR needs. I was empowered with skill and knowledge on how to use social media to advocate for Sexual Reproductive Health Rights for young people which has made me a very popular blogger'),
	(5433,821,'_content_3_big_quote','field_598162898cabf'),
	(5434,821,'content_3_quote_author','Mark Muganga, Peer Educator, 2015'),
	(5435,821,'_content_3_quote_author','field_5981629e8cac0'),
	(5436,821,'content_4_list_title','Why be part of Peer Education Academy'),
