	(7112,982,'_content_3_list_title','field_5981dfdb1b766'),
	(7113,982,'content_3_list_description','Our vision reminds us everyday that it is the young person were doing this for. We aim to live in a world where every young person is able to make life choices fully backed by the availability of information.\r\n\r\nWith this in mind, the Reach A Hand mission is to empower young people in Uganda aged 12-24 years with complete information, skills and tools which enable them live healthy, focused and productive lives.\r\n\r\nWe envision a young generation making informed choices in life. '),
