	(7129,982,'content_3_list_items_3_text','<p><strong>Appreciation of diversity</strong></p><p>We appreciate the difference in the social, cultural and political orientation, of its beneficiaries and endlessly works to promote understanding while recognizing the existent differences in its membership and beneficiaries. RAHU recognizes the universal nature and cross-cultural appreciation of human beings and rights.</p>'),
