	(7668,985,'_content_3_list_items_0_image','field_5981df9934d9b'),
	(7669,985,'content_3_list_items_0_text','<p><strong>Belief in young people</strong></p><p>we recognize that young peoples concerns can only be well addressed by young people and hence our slogan Young People for Young People</p>'),
	(7670,985,'_content_3_list_items_0_text','field_5981dfa034d9c'),
	(7671,985,'content_3_list_items_1_image','889'),
	(7672,985,'_content_3_list_items_1_image','field_5981df9934d9b'),
	(7673,985,'content_3_list_items_1_text','<p><strong>Youth driven</strong></p><p>We work with young people for young people, and brings in the spirit of volunteerism of young people.</p>'),
	(7674,985,'_content_3_list_items_1_text','field_5981dfa034d9c'),
	(7675,985,'content_3_list_items_2_image','857'),
	(7676,985,'_content_3_list_items_2_image','field_5981df9934d9b'),
	(7677,985,'content_3_list_items_2_text','<p><strong>Transparency and openness</strong></p><p>We believe in a culture of honesty and therefore employ an open door policy where all staff and volunteers can freely communicate with each other.</p>'),
	(7678,985,'_content_3_list_items_2_text','field_5981dfa034d9c'),
	(7679,985,'content_3_list_items_3_image','856'),
	(7680,985,'_content_3_list_items_3_image','field_5981df9934d9b'),
	(7681,985,'content_3_list_items_3_text','<p><strong>Appreciation of diversity</strong></p><p>We appreciate the difference in the social, cultural and political orientation, of its beneficiaries and endlessly works to promote understanding while recognizing the existent differences in its membership and beneficiaries. RAHU recognizes the universal nature and cross-cultural appreciation of human beings and rights.</p>'),
	(7682,985,'_content_3_list_items_3_text','field_5981dfa034d9c'),
	(7683,985,'content_3_list_items_4_image','861'),
	(7684,985,'_content_3_list_items_4_image','field_5981df9934d9b'),
	(7685,985,'content_3_list_items_4_text','<p><strong>Team work</strong></p><p>We believe team effort achieves much more than an individual work and therefore promote team work, utilizing each persons competences to achieve the overall organizational goals and objectives</p>'),
	(7686,985,'_content_3_list_items_4_text','field_5981dfa034d9c'),
