	(7859,986,'content_3_list_description','Our vision reminds us everyday that it is the young person were doing this for. We aim to live in a world where every young person is able to make life choices fully backed by the availability of information.\r\n\r\nWith this in mind, the Reach A Hand mission is to empower young people in Uganda aged 12-24 years with complete information, skills and tools which enable them live healthy, focused and productive lives.'),
