	(9718,1058,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Young people have worked so hard in transforming their communities at the point of being inspired by international acts who are willing to work with them in helping the transformation of different Communities in Uganda . Kudos to Reach A Hand Uganda (RAHU) members you will be joined by <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/officialnyanda?directed_target_id=0\"><span class=\"s2\"><b>Nyanda</b></span></a> who has accepted to be our Goodwill Ambassador.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">NYANDA is one half of the Pop/Reggae duo Brick &amp; Lace. They exploded onto the charts with singles Love is Wicked and Bad to Di Bone. Love is Wicked spent over 48 weeks on European Charts and catapulted NYANDA into the hearts of millions.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">In addition to being a great artist, NYANDA is a member of the prolific songwriting team Bloodline that penned the #1 Hit Follow The Leader for Jennifer Lopez and All Around The World for Christina Aguileira.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">\r\nNYANDA launched her solo career in 2013, and the response to her music has been overwhelming. Her 1st single, a reggae remix of Taylor Swift</span></p>'),
