	(9744,1060,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">RAHU has organised a full-time five-day youth camp YOURWAYS YOUTH HEALTH CAMP 2014 for the holiday makers and other youth who are not in school. The camp will take place at HANA Mixed School, Nsangi. It is meant to empower the youth to make informed choices.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The program will offer sexual health education and life skills training.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Participants from different school in Uganda and abroad are expected to attend.You can also register on line and reserve early.</span></p>'),
