	(9822,1066,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Rev. Canon Gideon Byamugisha is an Anglican priestin Uganda with a parish outside Kampala. Being the first religious leader in Africa to publicly announce His HIV status being Positive. Hes also recognised of his work to uphold the dignity and human rights of people living with HIV/AIDS.</span><span class=\"s1\"></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Rev. Byamugisha having become prominent in the international HIV/AIDS community has travelled internationally to speak about HIV?AIDS and Reach a Hand Uganda is as well honoured to have him among the keynote speakers at the  Your Way Youth Health Camp 2014.</span></p>'),
