	(9926,1074,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Just a few weeks before the 2014 MTV Africa Music Awards take place, MTV Base has revealed the MTV Base Leadership Award nominees. And our own Nabimanya Humphrey is among the the nominees.</span></p>\r\nThe award is given to a young African under the age of 35, through their leadership and contribution, is making a positive impact towards the growth and development of Africa across a broad spectrum of disciplines.\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The nominees are Ashish Thakkar (Tanzania); Humphrey Nabimanya (Uganda); Ludwick Marishane (South Africa); Dr Sandile Kubheka (South Africa) and Toyosi Akerele (Nigeria).</span></p>\r\nThe #MTVMAMAs will take place on 7 June in Durban, South Africa!\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s2\">Click <a href=\"http://www.mtvbase.com/news/mtv-base-leadership-award-nominees-revealed/\"><span class=\"s3\">here for details</span></a></span></p>'),
