	(10146,1093,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">I have volunteered with RAHU since 2011 and I have seen it grow as evidenced through the different events, activities and set strategies in RAHU, I can truly say; I have had an amazing experience working with it and it has partly made me who I am today.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Through RAHUs Peer Educators Academy that kicked off earlier in January 2014, I got to learn a lot from the different mentors who set the youth development strategies high hence benefiting much more to what was expected.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">RAHUs out reaches have also been a great deal to me and actually an amazing experience because they have groomed me into someone who can speak out to a large crowd with full confidence, which was not the case in the days before I joined RAHU, on that note I credit RAHU for that.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">And then came the camp, being among those who tasted RAHUs first sleep away camp in a period of six nights and five days introductory and learning sessions, I can gladly say everything came out successful through a lot of involvement and participation amongst campers, partners and the inspirational speakers who were part of the main drivers of the camp.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">It was such another new amazing experience and therefore congratulate RAHU upon that and also on how far it has reached.</span></p>'),
