	(10352,1105,'content_1_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">\"<b>Kaleke Kasome</b>\" is a song originally sang by Maurice Hasa. The remix is Part of the Reach a Hand Uganda Musical Project. The remix features Maurice Hasa himself, GNL Zamba, <a href=\"http://www.reachahand.org/news-and-media/165-jody-phibi-joins-rahu-cultural-icons\"><span class=\"s2\">JodyPhibi </span></a>(From Rwanda) and Ray Signature. The Kaleke Kasome Remix Video is officially out and already receiving massive air play on all local TV Stations. RAHU Musical Project is supported by Rutgers WPF and it so far includes Kaleke Kasome<b>, </b>Your ways and many other educative songs to come.</span></p>'),
