	(11020,1160,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">In an effort to have a systematic approach to monitoring and evaluating RAHU programs and the need to develop sufficient standards and criteria for determining what works, how and why in different situations and contexts, Reach A Hand Uganda seeks to hire a Monitoring and Evaluation consultant to support the process of developing an M&amp;E system inclusive of a customized database to aid in the capturing and analysing of data, information and project results. Such information and knowledge is critical for learning and identifying best practices for high quality programming.</span></p>'),
