	(11520,1215,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Across the world on every March 21, the world comes together to celebrate poetry in all its glory.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">No set rules are laid down for how to mark it. Be it any topic, you can read some poetry. You can perform it. You can write a poem. You can pop along and listen to someone read theirs.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Because poetry is wonderful. Its pure emotion and truth. And no matter who you are, theres a poem out there that will touch you the same way we would love this to appeal to you</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">To inspire you to fall back in love with poetry, our peer educator <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100007352083758&amp;fref=ts\"><span class=\"s2\">Shawn Davis Kawalya</span></a> has rounded up a poem about safe sex which you should be interested in reading. Check it out;</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h2 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>NO SAFE SEX, NO SEX</b></span></h2>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">I ask you to use it</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">And you reply \"No\"</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">I tell you that we won\'t have sex</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">And you reply \"So\"</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Is that how you feel?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">You don\'t want to because of that?</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">I thought you loved me</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">But I guess you were just talkin\' smack</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">I want to be safe</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">And you have a problem with it</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">You want to do it bare</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">But I don\'t know who you\'ve been with</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">We go back and forth</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">For a real long time</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">You are listening to your opinion</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">And I am listening to mine</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">You say live sex</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">I say safe sex</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">You keep saying live sex</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">And now there will be no sex</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Five years later</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">You calling me from a clinic</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Telling me everything</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">That you got from some belle</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">I cry for you inside</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">Because I feel bad for you</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">If you would\'ve listened 2 me back then</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s1\">You would not be where you are now, Boo</span></p>'),
