	(11860,1245,'content_2_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><b>To everyone else who made it possible</b></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p2\"><span class=\"s2\">Special thanks go to the Global Livingston Institute, <a href=\"http://www.segalfamilyfoundation.org/\"><span class=\"s3\">Segal Family Foundation</span></a>, <a href=\"https://ug.usembassy.gov/\"><span class=\"s3\">US Mission in Kampala</span></a>, <a href=\"http://www.aidshealth.org/\"><span class=\"s3\">AIDS Healthcare Foundation</span></a>,<a href=\"http://www.aicug.org/\"><span class=\"s3\"> AIDS Information Center</span></a>, <a href=\"http://www.rhu.or.ug/\"><span class=\"s3\">Reproductive Health Uganda</span></a>, <a href=\"http://mariestopes.or.ug/\"><span class=\"s3\">Marie Stopes Uganda</span></a>, <a href=\"http://www.ohlinc.org/\"><span class=\"s3\">Odyssey House Louisiana</span></a>, <a href=\"http://www.metairiebank.com/\"><span class=\"s3\">Metairie Bank</span></a>, <a href=\"https://ultramobile.com/\"><span class=\"s3\">Ultra Mobile</span></a>, <a href=\"http://www.entusi.org/\"><span class=\"s3\">Entusi Resort and Retreat Center</span></a>, <a href=\"http://www.nbs.ug/\"><span class=\"s3\">NBS Television</span></a> and <a href=\"http://www.eventswarehouse.biz/\"><span class=\"s3\">Events Warehouse</span></a>. You guys are awesome and thank you for making this happen.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Stay glued on our online media sites as we will be bringing you updates on our World AIDS Day 2016 commemoration activities in December. You wouldnt want to miss out on this one. Clue; One week to December.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Until then!</span></p>'),
