	(12200,1291,'content_0_content','<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Reach A Hand, Uganda (RAHU) and Communication for Development Foundation Uganda (CDFU) through Government of Uganda, UNFPA 8th Country Programme are seeking to contract a firm to develop a Music Video to popularize our latest audio song through the Musical Project aimed at increasing awareness on teenage pregnancy and under-age marriage.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">The video of the song targeting 12-24 year olds, must aim at amplifying the sexual reproductive health and rights (SRHR) messages in the audio, tell the story, challenges and experiences of young people in SRHR.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Do you think your firm or studio has got what it takes? Check out the terms of reference below and follow instructions to apply.\r\n</span></p>'),
